03:06.760 --> 03:08.590
- ♪ And add a little glitter ♪

03:08.670 --> 03:10.170
- ♪ The yard's
in a cloud of dust ♪

03:10.230 --> 03:11.860
- ♪ And you got, you got ♪

03:11.940 --> 03:13.610
- ♪ A game changer,
a player maker ♪

03:13.670 --> 03:15.040
♪ Take the ball,
she'll see it there ♪

03:15.110 --> 03:17.280
- ♪ I'm on a dream like team
like living ♪

