11:15.150 --> 11:16.960
But they were over it
by the time you came in.

11:17.020 --> 11:19.560
Right, guys?

11:19.620 --> 11:21.650
- Uh, yeah.

11:21.730 --> 11:23.500
I'm totally over it, coach.

11:23.560 --> 11:25.860
- I was over it even
before he was over it.

11:25.930 --> 11:27.930
- Oh, yeah, well, I feel--

11:28.000 --> 11:32.140
- Anyway...coach,
you put me in charge.

11:32.200 --> 11:36.980
So why don't you trust me
on this and let me lead?

11:37.040 --> 11:40.250
Also I can wash your
car for you later.

11:40.310 --> 11:42.180
- Well, I mean, it would be
a shame to suspend

11:42.250 --> 11:44.050
my two best receivers
for a little--

11:44.110 --> 11:46.110
- Thing that will
never happen again.

11:46.180 --> 11:48.280
I personally guarantee it.

11:48.350 --> 11:49.990
Trust me.

11:50.050 --> 11:50.910
Show 'em.

11:50.990 --> 11:52.320
Hug it out.

11:57.590 --> 11:59.990
See?

12:00.060 --> 12:01.320
Okay, that's enough.

12:01.400 --> 12:02.600
- Get out, get out.

12:02.670 --> 12:05.840
Get out, before
I change my mind.

12:05.900 --> 12:07.730
Dawson?

12:08.940 --> 12:10.610
It's the white SUV.

12:10.670 --> 12:13.170
It has a bumper sticker
"I brake for snickerdoodles."

12:18.850 --> 12:20.190
- That was close.

12:20.250 --> 12:21.890
But at least I got you
guys out of that mess.

12:21.950 --> 12:23.250
Now let's work this out.

12:23.320 --> 12:24.690
- Look, I've already
worked it out.

12:24.760 --> 12:27.130
If you don't make me the
number-one receiver tomorrow,

12:27.190 --> 12:28.460
I quit.

12:28.530 --> 12:29.890
- And if you don't make me
the number-one receiver,

12:29.960 --> 12:30.730
then I quit.

12:30.790 --> 12:31.550
- What?

12:31.630 --> 12:33.600
I--I can't choose between you.

12:33.660 --> 12:35.190
- Come on, Newt, we're
going to the Starcade.

12:35.270 --> 12:36.470
- No, Newt, come with me.

12:36.530 --> 12:37.760
