I'm stuck in the middle.

16:52.890 --> 16:53.590
Oh, no.

16:53.660 --> 16:55.630
Who's got me this weekend?

16:55.690 --> 16:57.600
- I've tried everything
to get them on the team.

16:57.660 --> 16:59.130
But it's impossible.

16:59.200 --> 17:02.700
Those guys are such stubborn,
competitive boneheads.

17:02.770 --> 17:04.339
- It's not about
football, Bella.

17:04.400 --> 17:05.540
It's about friendship.

17:05.599 --> 17:07.000
They've been inseparable since
the first day

17:07.069 --> 17:09.770
at peewee football camp.

17:09.839 --> 17:11.280
- You're right.

17:11.339 --> 17:12.980
I've been looking
at this the wrong way.

17:13.040 --> 17:16.470
If I want to save the team,
I've gotta save the friendship.

17:16.550 --> 17:17.950
- Do it fast, Bella.

17:18.010 --> 17:19.440
Ever since they broke up, I've
been having nightmares

17:19.520 --> 17:21.349
about the goat man.

17:21.420 --> 17:24.359
His hairy legs, his horns

17:24.420 --> 17:28.060
and his hoofs and--

17:28.130 --> 17:30.060
- We've barely sold anything.

17:30.130 --> 17:32.060
