options that are all so good.

17:45.780 --> 17:47.580
I can't even decide what's best.

17:47.640 --> 17:48.700
- Sounds good.

17:48.780 --> 17:51.120
I'll give you five bucks
for one of each.

17:51.180 --> 17:52.550
- Six.

